it\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5 stabdh\xc4\x81 dhanam\xc4\x81namad\xc4\x81nvit\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5  \nyajante n\xc4\x81mayaj\xc3\xb1ais te dambhen\xc4\x81vidhip\xc5\xabrvakam 16.17  \n  \naha\xe1\xb9\x83k\xc4\x81ra\xe1\xb9\x83 bala\xe1\xb9\x83 darpa\xe1\xb9\x83 k\xc4\x81ma\xe1\xb9\x83 krodha\xe1\xb9\x83 ca  \nsa\xe1\xb9\x83\xc5\x9brit\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5  \nm\xc4\x81m \xc4\x81tmaparadehe\xe1\xb9\xa3u pradvi\xe1\xb9\xa3antobhyas\xc5\xabyak\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5 16.18  \n  \nt\xc4\x81n aha\xe1\xb9\x83 dvi\xe1\xb9\xa3ata\xe1\xb8\xa5 krur\xc4\x81n sa\xe1\xb9\x83s\xc4\x81re\xe1\xb9\xa3u nar\xc4\x81dham\xc4\x81n  \nk\xe1\xb9\xa3ip\xc4\x81my ajasram a\xc5\x9bubh\xc4\x81n \xc4\x81sur\xc4\xab\xe1\xb9\xa3v eva yoni\xe1\xb9\xa3u 16.19  \n  \n\xc4\x81sur\xc4\xab\xe1\xb9\x83 yonim \xc4\x81pann\xc4\x81 m\xc5\xab\xe1\xb8\x8dh\xc4\x81 janmanijanmani  \nm\xc4\x81m apr\xc4\x81pyaiva kaunteya tato y\xc4\x81nty adham\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 gatim  \n16.20  \n  \ntrividha\xe1\xb9\x83 narakasyeda\xe1\xb9\x83 dv\xc4\x81ra\xe1\xb9\x83 n\xc4\x81\xc5\x9banam \xc4\x81tmana\xe1\xb8\xa5  \nk\xc4\x81ma\xe1\xb8\xa5 krodhas tath\xc4\x81 lobhas tasm\xc4\x81d etat traya\xe1\xb9\x83  \ntyajet 16.21  \n  \netair vimukta\xe1\xb8\xa5 kaunteya tamodv\xc4\x81rais tribhir nara\xe1\xb8\xa5  \n\xc4\x81caraty \xc4\x81tmana\xe1\xb8\xa5 \xc5\x9breyas tato y\xc4\x81ti par\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 gatim 16.22  \n  \nya\xe1\xb8\xa5 \xc5\x9b\xc4\x81stravidhim uts\xe1\xb9\x9bjya vartate k\xc4\x81mak\xc4\x81rata\xe1\xb8\xa5  \nna sa siddhim av\xc4\x81pnoti na sukha\xe1\xb9\x83 na par\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 gatim  \n16.23  \n  \ntasm\xc4\x81c ch\xc4\x81stra\xe1\xb9\x83 pram\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x87a\xe1\xb9\x83 te  \nk\xc4\x81ry\xc4\x81k\xc4\x81ryavyavasthitau  \nj\xc3\xb1\xc4\x81tv\xc4\x81 \xc5\x9b\xc4\x81stravidh\xc4\x81nokta\xe1\xb9\x83 karma kartum ih\xc4\x81rhasi  \n16.24  \n  \n\n* * *\n\n[Next: XVII. atha saptada\xc5\x9bodhy\xc4\x81ya\xe1\xb8\xa5. (\xc5\x9braddh\xc4\x81trayavibh\xc4\x81gayoga\xe1\xb8\xa5)](bgs17.htm)\n\n'